org.apache.flink.contrib.tweetinputformat.model.places

类 Places

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.contrib.tweetinputformat.model.places.Places

  • public class Places
extends Object
    Places are specific, named locations with corresponding geo Coordinates. They can be attached to Tweet by specifying a place_id when tweeting.
    Tweet associated with places are not necessarily issued from that location but could also potentially be about that location.
    Tweet can be searched for. Tweets can also be found by place_id.
